Module com.example.organizer
Package com.bookclub.mao

Class RSVPMAO

java.lang.Object
com.bookclub.mao.RSVPMAO
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.bookclub.iao.IRSVPAO
public class RSVPMAO extends Object implements com.bookclub.iao.IRSVPAO
Mock Access Object (MAO) implementation for managing RSVP records. This class provides methods to retrieve, add, update, and delete RSVP entries from an in-memory list.
